{"type":"message","id":"a92edad5","parentId":"8680a384","timestamp":"2026-03-19T05:55:26.184Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The context usage is at 21% (41k/200k), which is well below the 60% threshold. The script's log would show \"Context usage normal: 21%\". No alert is needed - everything is fine.","thinkingSignature":"1d20c1b09e58f0e3b35b80e5ea2718938610b116ecad87c47e03c4dbbed41974"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>Context Monitor: ✅ 正常运行\n\n- **当前 Token 使用率:** 21% (41k/200k) — 远低于 60% 阈值\n- **会话状态:** 正常，无需干预\n\n一切就绪，Sir。🎩</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1362,"output":111,"cacheRead":37002,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38475,"cost":{"input":0.00040859999999999996,"output":0.00013319999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00111006,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0016518599999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773899722111}}
